name: Flikken Rotterdam
overview: Flikken Rotterdam takes place in Rotterdam, and is after Flikken Maastricht the second Dutch spin-off of the Flemish show Flikken.

production_companies.name: Warner Bros. International Television Production Netherlands

episodes.name: Slachter
episodes.overview: Detective Ben Slachter gets in trouble after an encounter with a home invader. Meanwhile, the other detectives respond to a drug-related call, but find themselves in an equally troublesome situation. As everyone deals with their difficulties, newly arrived public prosecutor Berg makes things even more complicated.
